snippet.title: NO T!ME NO SPACE - Let's Play!
snippet.description:
Capture the antimatter particles to unlock secret portals into different dimensions.

Play now:  https://redmagicblue.itch.io/notimenospace

Recommended browser: Firefox / Safari

A 3D FPS Shooter built with love in A-Frame.

A HTML5 video game created by Sara Ferro & Chris Weil

for Smartphone, Tablet, Laptop and PC.
Running on Windows, Mac, Linux, Android and iOS.

Developer: RedMagicBlue
Publisher: Artoldo Media
